      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Complete self-contained apartment units or extensions to a house created within, or with minor exterior additions to existing single-family homes, usually with their own separate entrances and generally for relatives of the homeowners.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
